data.description:
New Subdivision in Clay County. This home is located on an oversized lot that backs up to a wooded area. 5 Bedrooms with 4 Full Baths and Bonus Room located upstairs.
Luxury Vinyl Flooring in living areas.  Carpet in all bedrooms. Granite Countertops in Kitchen and Quartz in all Baths. Solor panels to help reduce electric bill. Tankless HWH, piped in Gas.   Hook ups for Electric or Gas can be used on appliances.
